text:
"Arre tandon, yeh dabbe chhupale, woh senior log bahut maar rhe hain"
"Kya, dabbe toh mai rakhunga"
"Bhai dekhle, aise hi kuch lafda ho"
"Abe kyu bolenge dabbon ka kuch?"
"Bhai pata nhi mujhe "
*after a while*
" Abe chutiye, kitni baar bola unhone dabba laptop ko kehte hain woh, food contatiners ko nhi"
author: Rijul  Tandon

text: Aur jo bhi ho, pajame ka naada achhe se baandho.
author: Rijul  Tandon
